# Decision: <%= @decision.question %>

| created_at | <%= @decision.created_at %> |
| updated_at | <%= @decision.updated_at %> |
| deadline | <%= @decision.deadline %> |
| time remaining | <%= @decision.deadline > Time.now ? distance_of_time_in_words(Time.now, @decision.deadline) : 'Deadline passed' %> |

<% if @decision.description.present? -%>
## Description

<%= @decision.description %>
<% end -%>
<% unless @decision.closed? -%>
<% if @current_user && @decision.created_by && UserBlock.between?(@current_user, @decision.created_by) -%>
*Voting is unavailable because <% if @current_user.blocked?(@decision.created_by) %>you have blocked the author<% else %>you have been blocked by the author<% end %> of this decision.*
<% else -%>
## Options

<% if @decision.options.empty? -%>
No options yet.
<% else -%>
Check ✅ all options that you would accept. Star ⭐️ options you prefer.

<% @decision.options.order(:created_at).each do |option| -%>
<% vote = @votes.where(option: option).first || Vote.new(accepted: 0) -%>
* [<%= vote.accepted == 1 ? '✅' : ' ' %>] [<%= vote.preferred == 1 ? '⭐️' : ' ' %>] <%= option.title %>
<% end -%>
<% end -%>
<% end -%>
<% end -%>
## <%= @decision.closed? ? "Final" : "Current" %> Results

Results are sorted first by acceptance ✅, then by preference ⭐, then by random digits 🎲.

|   |   | ✅ | ⭐ | 🎲 |
|---|---|---|---|---|
<% if @decision.results.empty? -%>
| 0 | Add options to see results. | 0 | 0 | 0 |
<% end -%>
<% @decision.results.each.with_index do |result, index| -%>
| <%= index + 1 %> | <%= result.option_title %> | <%= (result.accepted_yes || 0) %> | <%= (result.preferred || 0) %> | <%= result.random_id.slice(0, 3) + "..." %> |
<% end -%>

## Voters (<%= @decision.voters.count %>)

<% if @decision.voters.empty? -%>
No voters yet.
<% else -%>
<% @decision.voters.each do |voter| -%>
* <%= user_link_md(voter) %>
<% end -%>
<% end -%>
<%= render 'shared/backlinks', resource: @decision %>
<%= render 'shared/attachments_section', resource: @decision %>
<%= render 'shared/comments_section', resource: @decision %>

